{"title":"AMBOSS. Leucemias agudas","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/AMBOSS. Leucemias agudas-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Leucemias agudas","guid":"iv2mxDaCzooH6BcB1rpwNg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"- **Leucemia aguda**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Enfermedades neoplásicas malignas","guid":"xMAMk5AqtFPn4Hm5WCFjJQ","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"- Origen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"- Línea linfoide → Leucemia linfoblástica aguda (LLA)","guid":"mjQxqguLwCA63ZX9cnqsBw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"- Línea mieloide → Leucemia mieloide aguda (LMA)","guid":"-teB3QMebRctjOmyt0QFEg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"## EPIDEMIOLOGÍA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"- **Leucemia\\Nlinfoblástica aguda\\N(LLA)**","guid":"RqhlSHNBeeXcUXUr0RW9pg","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"- Incidencia máxima: 2-5 años","guid":"snRL-CR_CCTKar-WK4IFIQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"- Enfermedad maligna más común en niños","guid":"n3rWS1a1QuApbiqE57MSuA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"- ~80% de leucemias agudas en la infancia son linfoblásticas","guid":"3RMaVkubRPZ9SsoifidWrA","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"- ♂ > ♀","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"6","text":"- **Leucemia mieloide\\Naguda (LMA)**","guid":"sJLRihSGeYJtLen-9N8BOQ","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"- Incidencia máxima: 65 años","guid":"XgDfvUY-vfzs6bo-POLaIw","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"- 80% de las leucemias agudas en adultos son mielógenas","guid":"pRVJNRL3KCCzSv9ibZ8uUg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"0","text":"## ETIOLOGÍA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"- **Leucemia\\Nlinfoblástica aguda\\N(LLA)**","guid":"ImYBhczHq-eoTvrvFExnlQ","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"- Sin causa o factores de riesgo identificables en la mayoría de casos","guid":"Bt49wGiNtWVs7krh1dq8Rg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"- Daño previo de médula ósea por quimioterapia alquilante o radiación ionizante","guid":"2F22xBdwmLTxjbWae3lNqg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"- Leucemia/linfoma de células T del adulto: vinculada a infección por HTLV","guid":"49xypf2Ad9g3M66MrZRzAg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"16","text":"- Factores genéticos o\\Ncromosómicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"- Síndrome de Down: riesgo 10-20 veces mayor","guid":"VkYtZ9x9JMat7dkWk2xe6g","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"- Neurofibromatosis tipo 1","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"- Ataxia telangiectasia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"15","text":"- **Leucemia mieloide\\Naguda (LMA)**","guid":"PDogS_epbP1WoZbbK0uT8Q","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"- Sin causa o factores de riesgo identificables en la mayoría de casos","guid":"9DtuqAuWdCvjMaJHzTEDGQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"- Trastorno hematopoyético preexistente\\N(causa identificable más común)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"- Síndromes mielodisplásicos","guid":"-e-uSSplWmcxQHU8ysM9LA","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"- Anemia aplásica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"- Trastornos mieloproliferativos (osteomielofibrosis, LMC)","guid":"PfMQib8nvsBJdoEhbHvKvA","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"24","text":"- Factores ambientales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"- Quimioterapia alquilante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"- Radiación ionizante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"- Exposición a benceno","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"- Tabaco","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"24","text":"- Factores genéticos o\\Ncromosómicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"- Síndrome de Down: riesgo 10-20 veces mayor (especialmente M7 en pacientes con Down)","guid":"o_bX9nAkHTSB1DJzq85f1w","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"- Anemia de Fanconi","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"0","text":"## CLASIFICACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"- **LLA**","guid":"_8vHPOLF4yy859vkgafPow","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"- Clasificación histórica\\NFranco-Americana-Británica (FAB) de\\NLLA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"- L1: LLA con células\\Npequeñas (20-30%)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"- Típico linfocito chiquito","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"- Relación núcleo-citoplasma muy alta, casi sin citoplasma","guid":"2kJ_Uzxc4-nkV8QwHsOLxg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"- Con nucléolo en su interior","guid":"2edvmRqIG8TUSzXhdDnsUw","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"- Suele confundirse con prolinfocitos","guid":"ImyufDb-kepk3kWrItD8qA","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"40","text":"- L2: LLA con células grandes\\Nheterogéneas (70%)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"- Célula con más nucléolo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"- Relación núcleo-citoplasma un poco más baja","guid":"RoY6yXi_HHFjtci9PQknrQ","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"- Célula más grande que L1","guid":"BCpXcpiUHA9iKWlDDC_5Yw","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"40","text":"- L3: LLA con células grandes,\\Nlinfoma de Burkitt (1-2%)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"- Células con vacuolas","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"39","text":"- Clasificación de Tumores\\NHematolinfoides de la OMS (2022)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"- Leucemias/linfomas linfoblásticos de células B:\\NLLA de células B (~80-85% de LLA)","guid":"b5rstZ11MW0aTOsk-_sk1A","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"- LLA-B categorizada por hallazgos citogenéticos o genéticos","guid":"9KgiNSXTnDpX8wl84_kqxA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"- LLA-B con hiperdiploidía alta","guid":"P_ejRJ-soy5-KvHe_yO8pA","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"- LLA-B con BCR-ABL1","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"53","text":"- LLA-B con ETV6-RUNX1","guid":"EnkfcESmbB3JlV6-oTsTrA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"53","text":"- LLA-B con otras anomalías genéticas definidas","guid":"elvxBF7YAiabXnjs0BQ8Kg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"53","text":"- LLA-B no especificada de otra manera","guid":"HFwsmaSv4qBUWewj3ix_mQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"52","text":"- Leucemias/linfomas linfoblásticos de células T:\\NLLA de células T (~15-20% de LLA)","guid":"LY26q5diQnxbGF9UVxcdjQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"- LLA de precursores T tempranos","guid":"jbsjvditjFv97R_bWpdjZw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"38","text":"- **LMA**","guid":"2LSjdhrTRZeI4ljn7UMDdQ","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"- Clasificación\\NFranco-Americana-Británica\\N(FAB)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"- M0-LMA: Leucemia mieloblástica\\Naguda sin maduración","guid":"LKgul5TJiNL6xEng_rtvLw","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"- Células plásticas difíciles de clasificar","guid":"vSMP_puFcUsIVdXLUP8ciQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"- Difícil determinar si son linfoides o mieloides","guid":"twAayD7N6wY6-7SWcXl6-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"63","text":"- M1-LMA: Leucemia mieloblástica aguda\\Ncon maduración granulocítica mínima","guid":"rKSZYdtPKCYeCwb2Uj7dNQ","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"- Estirpe más mieloide pero aún difícil de diferenciar","guid":"B_qj2dHzqi66zwVRbkXSEw","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"- Puede secretar mieloperoxidasa","guid":"qsnP4ai1GtkuHauQjXzXXQ","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"- Ayuda el citómetro pero morfológicamente difícil de detectar","guid":"FB7Kj1d5jPIM-D3sYluDug","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"63","text":"- M2-LMA: Leucemia mieloblástica aguda\\Ncon maduración granulocítica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"- Clásico blasto mieloide","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"- Célula más grande con relación núcleo-citoplasma más baja","guid":"OH6szzXwlI020v1z6tvaVg","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"- Citoplasma basófilo bastante azulado","guid":"Abs9Q5TcNBDF48b6_FTa3Q","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"71","text":"- Núcleo con nucleolo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"63","text":"- M3-LMA: Leucemia\\Npromielocítica aguda (LPA)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"- Promielocito característico","guid":"aNw5OWYw37c7u0LQQgvdmA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"- Célula grande con 2-3-4-5 nucléolos","guid":"iHjtbkqP13eUcQVfVZSpbw","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"- Llena de gránulos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"76","text":"- Bastones de Auer característicos","guid":"5KXUkLenUby8fdxmhq8MoQ","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"76","text":"- Única leucemia tratable 100% (>95% curable)","guid":"-vuEkZmLb77ySMVOURanhw","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"76","text":"- Gránulos se liberan y provocan coagulopatía","guid":"qPBtvIHvO4bCvBTlPt4NkQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"76","text":"- Requiere soporte intensivo y ATRA/trióxido de arsénico","guid":"cXvFFbUyDms9wDeIDqJLDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"63","text":"- M4-LMA: Leucemia mielomonocítica aguda","guid":"OgPz4MDFZ6QqIeXKdp1ZyA","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"63","text":"- M5-LMA: Leucemia monocítica aguda","guid":"t_kAH_GM_N719SFX1skwNA","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"- Se aprecia más citoplasma","guid":"yKAwCMH9JXNPjWh6bYrUEA","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"63","text":"- M6-LMA: Leucemia eritroide aguda","guid":"Dx0csXM7i4FERFP8qQVLAg","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"63","text":"- M7-LMA: Leucemia megacarioblástica aguda","guid":"fiwhHwcFE288gADU0hXCIQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"- Muy rara, más común en síndrome de Down","guid":"IErldONbM5qOx0WJxrlCJg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"62","text":"- Clasificación de Tumores\\NHematolinfoides de la OMS (2022)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"- LMA con anomalías genéticas definidas","guid":"JgbXmSnUM4OfoDFnlRFaUw","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"- LMA, definida por diferenciación","guid":"j5xKqgu4Zp4y4gg3hctesw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"- LMA, relacionada con mielodisplasia","guid":"450it1gQxop0pa2u2zqRgQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"- Sarcoma mieloide","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"90","text":"- Calificadores diagnósticos para\\Nneoplasias mieloides secundarias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"- Neoplasia mieloide post terapia citotóxica","guid":"bMy9UvyNiC0GIkXwlVS4CA","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"- Neoplasia mieloide asociada con predisposición germinal","guid":"GBr7a7sFEtqE5ApSx6XNjw","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"- Proliferación mieloide asociada al síndrome de Down","guid":"PSS1DLPsj6qJsgtoWwFy0A","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"## FISIOPATOLOGÍA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"- Mutaciones somáticas adquiridas\\N(translocaciones cromosómicas y\\Notras anomalías genéticas)","guid":"fYTnOj4nCjUf1mjcWyXByQ","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"→ Proliferación clonal de línea de células madre linfoide o mieloide","guid":"RGHB3TkmLgolMN4zOROHZA","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"→ Detención en diferenciación y maduración celular en etapas tempranas de hematopoyesis","guid":"mNY_csv-IYMlq-C2BWwb3A","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"→ Rápida proliferación de blastos anormales y disfuncionales (con vías de apoptosis alteradas)","guid":"hOY9nlufMkY5Ih1Z3Dw1pQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"→ Acumulación de leucocitos leucémicos en médula ósea","guid":"FwaFaaIxxUci-BkhuOOGKA","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"100","text":"→ Hematopoyesis normal interrumpida","guid":"Elw0qMIYsRBkK9IYPBFFpw","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"100","text":"→ Leucopenia (↑ riesgo de infecciones), trombocitopenia (↑ sangrado) y anemia","guid":"JytT0JX6aDILXzMX4jZbMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"99","text":"- Blastos inmaduros entran al torrente sanguíneo","guid":"BySZLiwB5OYZLfVdYpgIcg","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"→ Infiltración de otros órganos (particularmente SNC, testículos, hígado y piel)","guid":"ucs2n64U9q2eEVRY3ibFOg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"0","text":"##\\NCARACTERÍSTICAS\\NCLÍNICAS","guid":"bqi1r1JSMYwwe4_xOQe98Q","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"- **Características generales\\Nde leucemia aguda**","guid":"PiV7FprRPjMlZeJ5ultE5A","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"- Inicio súbito de síntomas y\\Nprogresión rápida (días a semanas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"- Anemia: fatiga,\\Npalidez, debilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"- Trombocitopenia: epistaxis, sangrado\\Nde encías, petequias, púrpura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"110","text":"- Leucocitos inmaduros:\\Ninfecciones frecuentes, fiebre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"110","text":"- Hepatoesplenomegalia (causada\\Npor infiltración leucémica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"110","text":"- Emergencias oncológicas como primer signo\\N(más común en LMA que LLA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"110","text":"- Todo paciente con leucemia\\Naguda debe recibir tratamiento\\Nempírico inmediato","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"110","text":"- Diferencia clave\\NLMA vs LLA:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"- LMA: necesita tratamiento\\Ninmediato, especialmente M3 (LPA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"- En LPA (M3): monitoreo de\\Ncoagulopatía (fibrinógeno, pruebas\\Nde coagulación cada 6h)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"- Soporte transfusional: plaquetas,\\Ncrioprecipitado si protrombina <60%","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"109","text":"- **Características\\Nclínicas específicas**","guid":"7D6jNRNxOlYzUPRxHrh_3Q","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"- **LLA**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"- Fiebre, sudores nocturnos, pérdida de peso inexplicada","guid":"cfqgs_t6xvR8D4iRCIZfPg","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"- Linfadenopatía indolora","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"- Dolor óseo (cojera o rechazo a soportar peso en niños)","guid":"Fxr3ZZTS_-Db_QR2ML47GQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"123","text":"- Obstrucción de vías respiratorias por infiltración mediastínica o tímica (principalmente LLA de células T)","guid":"6kCmkrSaeabTW9bL7qEj9g","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"123","text":"- Características de síndrome de VCS","guid":"eKhRX67JdsnV7NGaK14-VA","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"123","text":"- Leucemia meníngea: cefalea, rigidez de nuca, cambios en campo visual u otros síntomas del SNC","guid":"BEWua9LQOcwypXQIb7Ll6Q","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"123","text":"- Agrandamiento testicular (hallazgo raro)","guid":"37r13VabQaq2bQzGbfUSqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"122","text":"- **LMA**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"- Leucemia cutis (sarcoma mieloide): lesiones nodulares cutáneas de color púrpura o gris-azulado","guid":"NwYQ0jcN3U1CCdGnH-hW2A","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"13